{"tid":1784116,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"浙江籃球隊獅頭扮毛澤東遭重罰百萬","createTime":"2019-12-15T12:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T12:31:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cf527a4ec9e63b75040bb98eb5f0f986940adfbd","tid":1784116,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:13:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191214/ECD6PYP34PXBZGDEZIYWC5DL6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191214%2FECD6PYP34PXBZGDEZIYWC5DL6U%2F&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hk63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=31063344\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191214%2FECD6PYP34PXBZGDEZIYWC5DL6U%2F&h=a5319149\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191214/ECD6PYP34PXBZGDEZIYWC5DL6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n浙江籃球隊獅頭扮毛澤東遭重罰百萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191214/large/1576257520_ec90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191214%2Flarge%2F1576257520_ec90.jpg&h=c1546ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣廈隊一張文革風海報闖下大禍。<br />\n<br />\n中國男子籃球職業聯賽（CBA）浙江廣廈猛獅日前因推出了一張以中共前領導人毛澤東為設計靈感的海報，惟疑似遭到小粉紅「篤灰」，遭CBA開出史上最貴的100萬人民幣（約113萬港元）罰單，直接負責人更被處以終身禁止參加CBA相關工作的重罰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑被小粉紅篤灰<br />\n<br />\n據悉，猛獅日前在微博發佈對陣八一南昌的賽前海報，廣廈球隊的獅頭被拼接到文革時期毛澤東的經典畫像上，頭戴軍帽，上方幾個大字，「落後就要挨打」，海報下方有5名球員戴上紅領巾，風格酷似當年文革時期的宣傳海報。廣廈在發佈此圖時，在配文直呼「紅色精神永流傳」，似向中共致敬。<br />\n<br />\n不過，不少內地網友見狀痛斥海報「你詆毀了我們偉大的領導人」、「設計的人沒腦子」、「要是在以前肯定上槍斃名單第一位」，甚至有人認為海報「涉嫌侮辱先烈」。CBA官網在前日（12日）的新聞稿指出，廣廈的比賽海報出現了「嚴重不當訊息，造成了極其惡劣的社會影響」，並處罰廣廈直接責任人「終身禁止參加CBA聯賽相關工作」。廣廈隊則被取消本賽季評優資格、罰款100萬人民幣。<br />\n<br />\nCBA指出，聯賽內各球隊應在日常工作中「弘揚社會主義核心價值觀」，嚴格遵守國家法規和CBA的規定，推廣正能量並正面引導球迷。廣廈事後亦發出道歉聲明，承認設計、審核人員嚴重疏忽，「對公眾情感造成傷害」，事後已開除相關設計及審核人員，責令宣傳部門整改，杜絕此類事件再次發生。<br />\n<br />\nCBA官網/微博"},{"pid":"a7094e3ecf24cc929bcb5b2e35cac6881cc4aa42","tid":1784116,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDHdKiw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDHdKiw.jpg&h=779c8437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0890f1bc43a7f6810c9ffbb4b56bf45c479ad8a9","tid":1784116,"uid":300642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"百姓的錢就是黨的錢，何來罰錢之說？"},{"pid":"d204df135894df510650dad3c749f5f4ff9cf8d4","tid":1784116,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:16:21.000Z","msg":"落後就要挨打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5494cf81830e77e072476d3a9a76c4af349fd1ee","tid":1784116,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"真心問，觸犯左咩底線？"},{"pid":"a86d6e5f8725a43e27d0568be5050b44087593d2","tid":1784116,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:20:44.000Z","msg":"唔用文革風<br />\n咪用美帝風囉"},{"pid":"9e3bd62fa4d08297f40bba068571b012ed29bafd","tid":1784116,"uid":69309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:21:25.000Z","msg":"所以話大陸人邊有創作思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地歐美已經唔知玩左自己國旗幾多人<br />\n玻璃心到連張海報都包容唔到<br />\n好明顯係致敬多過惡搞啦<br />\n申利：覺得張圖幾好"},{"pid":"53e20fcb80d9dec061ec3c2f085a2a1140c10a0a","tid":1784116,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:23:28.000Z","msg":"地主要挨打<br />\n知識分子要挨打<br />\n有冇文宣組反攻大陸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae5cfa2c6719913b0dc009d249f4938cc99800b","tid":1784116,"uid":103936,"like":